snippet.title: SONIC X SHADOW GENERATIONS - Sonic the Hedgehog 3 Movie Pack Trailer
snippet.description:
Keanu is Shadow! Owners of the Digital Deluxe Edition of SONIC X SHADOW GENERATIONS can now dash through the streets of Shibuya in this unique stage inspired by the events of the Sonic the Hedgehog 3 movie!

SONIC X SHADOW GENERATIONS is out now: https://sonicxshadowgenerations.com/
